prompts.frontCover: A charming, humorous watercolor painting of a scruffy terrier dog wearing a ridiculously tiny, lopsided birthday party hat. The dog has a mischievous grin, one ear flopped down, and its head is tilted in a funny, confused way as it looks at a single, brightly colored cupcake with a lit candle sitting on the floor just out of reach. The dog's paws are planted firmly, as if it's contemplating its next move to get the treat. In the center, "Happy Birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script. The style is a flat 2D cartoon, with soft, flowing watercolor colors, visible artistic brushstrokes, subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds along the edges of the dog and cupcake, giving it a whimsical, hand-painted feel.
